Package org.testframe.api

Class AssertersTest

java.lang.Object
org.testframe.api.AssertersTest
public class AssertersTest extends Object
Tests of the Asserters class. These are more elegant than the tests of testframe.engine.TestRunner, but still more clunky than the tests that can be written once Asserters is fully tested and proven.

Because of the tests for assertTimeout(), this test class could take as much as ten seconds to run.

Author:
Alonso del Arte
